headline: Steel Dynamics Gives Weak Q4 Outlook, But Says Business Remains Solid
summary: Steel Dynamics warned that lower prices and shipments and an unplanned outage at a factory will affect current-quarter earnings.

headline: Steel Dynamics Provides Fourth Quarter 2024 Earnings Guidance
summary: Steel Dynamics, Inc. (NASDAQ/GS: STLD) today provided fourth quarter 2024 earnings guidance in the range of $1.26 to $1.30 per diluted share. Comparatively, the company's sequential third quarter 2024 earnings were $2.05 per diluted share, and prior year fourth quarter earnings were $2.61 per diluted share.
